# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]
- Add validations to check corner-cases in the service layer
- Dockerize the application

## [0.1.0]
### Added
- Polyglot database model to support the system (Postgres and ElasticSearch)
- Swagger to document the Rest API
- Test suites to check the service layer, mappers, and controllers
- Support for simple text processing using RabbitMQ as message broker
